data.description: This exquisite home offers not just a residence, but a lifestyle of convenience and luxury living. Located in the rare gem garden home neighborhood of Balcones Creek, where meticulously manicured front and back yards are tended to by the HOA, your time is liberated to indulge in what truly matters. Crafted by esteemed builder Sitterle Homes, quality and sophistication are woven into every corner of this dwelling. Step inside and experience the perfect fusion of elegance and functionality. An open floorplan beckons, inviting you to explore its spacious layout that effortlessly adapts to your every need. With flexible spaces that can seamlessly transform into a serene office, a vibrant gameroom, or a cozy TV lounge, this home caters to your desires. The foyer boasts a striking tiled barrel ceiling, a testament to the meticulous craftsmanship that defines this residence. Beautiful slate-look tile spans the floors, offering both durability and aesthetics. The heart of the home features an extra-large kitchen island, beckoning gatherings and culinary creations, surrounded by sleek cabinetry, gas cooking and top-tier appliances. High ceilings create an airy ambiance throughout, while plantation shutters adorn the windows, allowing you to control the natural light that filters in. Warmth emanates from the IPI gas fireplace surrounded by Texas rock, adding a touch of rustic charm to the contemporary living space. Each bedroom is a private retreat, boasting its own ensuite for unparalleled comfort and convenience.  A sanctuary of relaxation awaits outdoors - your very own private oasis. The extended patio, adorned with a charming fireplace and electric sun screens, offers a tranquil retreat for quiet mornings or enchanting evenings under the stars. Feel the stress melt away as you unwind in this exceptional outdoor haven. Venturing upstairs, you'll find a delightful surprise - a game room complete with a full bathroom and a Texas basement, providing both entertainment and practical storage options. Also included is a spacious three-car tandem garage, offering ample space for vehicles, storage, and more. Includes an EV charger, a green-minded feature that allows you to power up your electric vehicle effortlessly from the comfort of your home. Experience the harmonious blend of luxury, nature, and convenience in this extraordinary home. Embrace a carefree lifestyle and benefit from a community that offers access to a range of exclusive amenities, including a Jr. Olympic pool, clubhouse, children's play area, and a community garden as well as the convenience of nearby shopping, dining, and entertainment options, including the newest HEB - coming soon.
